name: "Pink & Blue Sweetness" Handmade Necklace
description: Very sweet necklace made on tan & pink suede leather using a beautiful big, blue bead from India, carved white shells and some pretty blue glass tubes and pink beads.

name: "Lemon & Pink Loveliness" Handmade Earrings
description:
I just adore these pale pink vintage baroque beads ~ one of my favourite finds ever! They remind me of twirling ballerinas.

Here I have paired them with unique pale yellow vintage Czech glass beads on sterling silver.

Simple and perfect.

name: "Turquoise, Turquoise Ocean" Handmade Necklace
description:
Large Turquoise gemstone pendant encased in oxidised sterling silver dangles amidst carved white shells, pretty 1940's milk glass and blue glass tubes on soft, brown, suede leather.

This is divine and has an adjustable leather strap to wear it long or short.

name: "Marshmallow & Jaffa Drops" Handmade Earrings
description:
Made with vintage 1950's jaffa (orange/red) round beads and new pink beads, sitting on sterling silver.

These reminded me of my dear friend, Marie who loves pink and red.

5/5 pairs made, with love.

name: "Lilac Love Birds" Handmade Necklace
description:
Pretty 1950's lucite lilac love birds dangle amidst 1940's milk beads & real carved shells on soft brown suede leather.

Lovely & long, perfect with your Sunday jeans & white flowing vintage blouse.

name: "Vintage Roses & Milk Glass" Handmade Earrings
description:
Adore these so much, I made a pair for myself too! 

I was able to find just 12 of these lovely 1950's glass vintage rose beads and have paired them with 1940's milk glass beads and bright yellow vintage beads from Japan on sterling silver.

They dangle ever so prettily, so unique & beautiful.

Best to be worn lots and lots to keep the silver shiny.

name: "Blue Carnival" Handmade Earrings
description: Beautiful 1950's Czech beads sitting on gold vermeil (sterling silver coated in gold), like a carnival by the sea ~ pretty blues!

name: "Sea & Sand" HANDMADE EARRINGS made with shell
description:
Inspired by the sea & sand, pretty blue and yellow handmade earrings using carved white shells, Lapis Lazuli gemstones & yellow swirled beads on sterling silver.

Long drops on beautiful hoops.

1/1 pair made.

name: "Nectarines in the Garden" HANDMADE EARRINGS
description:
So fresh and happy looking are this pair of earrings that remind my daughter of nectarines. Round bright beads sit against 1950's orange beads on sterling silver.

Simple shapes ~ fun & pretty. 

1/1 pair made

name: "Pretty Earth" Gemstone HANDMADE EARRINGS
description:
Earthy toned handmade earrings using Rhodochrosite faceted beads ~ a pretty, dusky pink toned rare gemstone, Lemon Chrysoprase squares and lemon swirled beads sitting ever so prettily on sterling silver hoops.

These are my favourite pair for 2013. 

1/1 pair made.

name: "Pink & Navy Drops" Handmade Earrings
description: Made with pink beads, Lapis Luzuli, Rose Quartz, sterling silver and lots of love. 1/1 pair made.

name: "Orange Drops" Handmade Earrings
description: Made with 1950's Czech + Japanese beads, Lapis Luzuli, sterling silver and lots of love. 1/1 pair made.

name: Floristry Class for One ~ How to Make a Hand-tied Bouquet
description:
Learn how to make a hand-tied bouquet and to care for cut flowers. 

This is recommended as an introduction to floristry and is advised as the first class you undertake out of the Trinkets & Roses collection of classes.

One-on-one instruction will be provided in your own home ~ Janmaree will come to you. Available in local Brisbane area only (Sunshine Coast included). 

All materials will be supplied and the lesson is for 1.5 hours. 

On check out, please leave your contact details so we can arrange your class with you.

To arrange a group booking ~ please call 0403 776 378 or email ~ janmaree@trinketsandroses.com.au 

Make a group booking (3 or more) and receive a 15% discounted rate: for hen's nights, birthday parties, craft get-togethers, children's parties ~ any occasion you can think of!

Learning floristry is fun ~ you will learn to present flowers to your family and friends and design arrangements for your home with a professional finish. 

Janmaree is a trained teacher and florist and here combines her skills to present these special classes.

name: Floristry Class for One ~ How to Make a Flower Arrangement in Pot
description:
Learn how to make a flower arrangement in a pot and to care for potted arrangements.

This class includes a beautiful Robert Gordon mixing bowl or Robert Gordon jug to make your arrangement in.

All materials will be supplied and the lesson is for 1.5 hours. 

On check out, please leave your contact details so we can arrange your class with you.

This is recommended as the second class to take after the "How to make a hand-tied bouquet" class. 

One-on-one instruction will be provided in your own home ~ Janmaree will come to you. Available in the local Brisbane area only (Sunshine Coast included).

To arrange a group booking ~ please call 0403 776 378 or email ~ janmaree@trinketsandroses.com.au

Make a group booking (3 or more) and receive a 15% discounted rate: for hen's nights, birthday parties, craft get-togethers, children's parties ~ any occasion you can think of!

Learning floristry is fun and you will learn to present flowers to your family and friends and design arrangements for your home with a professional finish.

Janmaree is a trained teacher and florist and here combines her skills to present these special classes.

name: "I'm in the Garden" Dream-Catcher Handmade Necklace
description:
Pretty and unique necklace for the beautiful spring/summer months. 

Made using floristry techniques with sweet vintage beads, rose quartz heart and pink and white polka dot ribbon. 

A necklace to catch sweet dreams for you. 

Made with love,1/1 made.

name: "Ballet in the Garden" Handmade Earrings
description:
THESE ARE MY FAVOURITES for Summer '12, just so simple and gorgeous. 

Pretty ballet pink baroque mid century (20th) beads from Czechoslovakia paired with vintage beads from Japan. 

Choice of two colours: ballet pink and black or ballet pink and orange. 

Sitting on pretty sterling silver hoops. 

You will receive 1 pair. 

"Everything is beautiful at the ballet"
 - A Chorus Line

name: "Cherry and Gingham" Handmade Necklace
description:
Carved rose made from the gemstone, Cherry Quartz, lovingly placed on navy and white gingham ribbon with hand stitched vintage Czech beads across front. 

So much fun, can be worn long or as featured, looped around twice. 

Special handmade gift for a loved one. 

1/1 made only.

name: "Lace & Bead" Necklace ~ Prettiness on a string
description:
So simple and pretty is this handmade lace necklace with one large, ceramic, handpainted floral bead as the centre piece. 

As you wish, wear it short or long, hand tie the lace at the back to form a bow, which sits so pretty!

name: "Pastel Love" Pretty Fresh Flowers in Ceramic Jug
description:
Prior to purchase kindly call ~ Janmaree on 0403 776 378 to arrange delivery of your arrangement. As we visit the markets to hand-pick your flowers, please allow time for her to arrange your order. 

Trinkets & Roses arrangements are known for being very fresh and will adorn the home for a longer period as a result of this design process.

So gorgeous-sweet is this petite bouquet wrapped in pink sitting in your choice of a pale pink or pale blue Robert Gordon jug. Your recipient will enjoy the beautiful ceramic jug long after the flowers have faded. 

The bouquet will be finished with beautiful wrapping and couture ribbons, a beautiful card with your personalised message and a complimentary bookmark containing flower care advice.

Delivery available from Redcliffe to Brisbane, Queensland.  

Please provide your email address at checkout and we will forward a photograph of the completed floral arrangement to you!

name: "Her Daintiness" Handmade Necklace ~ Delicate, Sweet & Lovely
description: ~ Sweetness and light you will be wearing this divine one-off design ~ Made with beautiful rose quartz ~ Measures 45cm length and will sit on your d'ecollet'e ~ Will be delivered beautifully gift wrapped ~ Made to measure available, kindly email to arrange and we will pop a custom order in our store for you. "As the delicate lace blew gracefully in and out of my window and as the gentle sun beamed on my journal, I felt an excitement in my heart, I was in love" ~ Her Daintiness is inspired by true love.

name: "Rose Love" Handmade Necklace ~ Made to Attract Love
description:
Beautiful necklace made from amazonite and rose quartz. 

A delicate design that emanates a feeling of healing. With the large, carved amazonite rose and pretty fabric flowers you will feel loved!

~ Amazonite is said to create feelings of power, inspire truth, sincerity, self love, communication, eloquence, integrity, trust, clarity, prophecy, openness and restore spiritual faith 

~ Rose Quartz is associated with helping one to feel self-acceptance, self love and personal worth  

~ Necklace measures 45cm in length & Amazonite Rose is 4cm in length & width

name: "Healing Pinks" ~ Pretty Handmade Gemstone Earrings
description:
~ Many compliments will come your way wearing these stand-out earrings measuring 6cm (2.4 inches) long 

~ You will be surprised how many different outfits you will be able to wear them with

~ Made with rare oval Rhodochrosite, a very pretty gemstone that is coloured pink, cream and charcoal along with fresh water pearls and mangano calcite...I have not come across such a pretty gemstone like this...really gorgeous!

~ Hooks are sterling silver 

~ Limited Edition design, 10 pairs made only. Each pair of earrings will arrived numbered, for example, 1/10.

~ Will be delivered beautifully gift wrapped

~ We can also organise your parcel to be sent with a beautiful card personalised with your message as a complimentary service. Just kindly email to arrange.
